d helping me with this kill early this year or late last year.  The first kill we got the rogue piece for our rogue.  We killed him on and off for the last few months maybe a total of 8 times.  It took us forever to learn to single pull him.  He would have the bard piece most of the time.  He never had another epic piece other than that.<br>
<br>
This last weekend we focused on him.  Friday night another guild was taking him out.  They said that the wiz piece didn't drop nor did the bard piece.  I can't remember if they said any epic piece dropped.<br>
<br>
Saturday morning I got the camp and the bard piece dropped and the mage piece dropped.<br>
<br>
Saturday evening I had the camp and another guy came in and I told him I had the camp and my guild was enroute and he called his guild.  Both our guilds got there at the same time.  They pulled all 4 freaking swirlspines AND phinny.  Killed us all, them first and then us.  We almost killed Phinny at that point.  After corpse retrieval we managed to be ready first so we killed Phinny.  You know, he had been holding 2 staffs in his hands and we were all so sure he'd ave staffs.  No epic drop.  He always holds a freaking staff and it's always been rods of malaisement or that enchanter rod.  So then we had the other guy saying he was going to petition because we stole his kill.  Puleeaaase.  I was there first to begin with.  Plus, what did he want?  The rods of malaisement?  He could have those.<br>
<br>
Sunday morning we finally learned how to SINGLE pull phinny.  It was awesome.  (For those that are clueless like I was - make sure that none of the seahorses see invis.  Send eye of zomm over the ridge and target Phinny.  Have the 4 top seahorses lulled and then cast a no damage spell on Phinny.  My bro is a pally and he would stun Phinny and Phinny would come up and we had him.)  No epic pieces dropped.<br>
<br>
I was discouraged and just going to drop the whole matter.  A guildmate called me and told me they had started camp and I should come because that guy from the night before was back.  I think this is what got me to log on.  So we killed Phinny that night and finally he had the freaking wizzy piece.  I need Venril Sathir now.  The broken golem was my first kill. <p>Renia - wizardess of Cazic-Thule<br>
Baroness of MoY who aspires to greatness (and may attain it one day).</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=elidaarruneweaver>Elidaar Runeweaver</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/8/03 3:59:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm57.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=462>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> 75 times, finally got the BCS!!!</span><hr size=1> Got my Blue Crystal Staff on the Tunare server, Monday April 18th 2003, after 75 attempts at Phinigel and too many Chanter wands and Mage staves to count...!<br>
<br>
A HUGE HUGE thank you to my brother Tolar, without whose help this would not have been possible! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :hat --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/pimp.gif ALT=":hat"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
